data.name: Bariantopia
data.desc:
(This card is always treated as a "Barian's" card.)
Your opponent cannot target "CXyz" monsters, "Number C" monsters, and "Number" monsters with a number between "101" and "107" in their names you control with card effects, also they cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects. Once per turn, if you Special Summon an Xyz Monster with a "Rank-Up-Magic" Spell's effect: You can target that Xyz Monster and 1 monster your opponent controls; attach that opponent's monster to that Xyz Monster as material.
